snippet.title: God of War: Ascension - Zeus God Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/god-of-war/?emcid=or-1s-412983

In God of War: Ascension Multiplayer align with the King of the Gods to be bewstowed powerful magic upon your weapons, and remind your opponents who is at the top of the chain.

Get in the God of War: Ascension Multiplayer Beta 1-week early! Discover an untold story on your quest for redemption. Join The Rise of the Warrior only at http://www.godofwar.com.

God of War: Ascension hits March 12, 2013. Pre-order now to get the Mythological Heroes Pack.

Visit our official site at http://www.godofwar.com
LIKE us on Facebok at http://www.facebook.com/godofwar
Follow us on Twitter at http://www.twitter.com/SonySantaMonica
